{"tid":2386648,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【入獄前專訪】癌症末期迎第十次政治監 古思堯:抗爭至死方休","createTime":"2021-01-29T17:15:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-30T02:30:56.000Z","uid":240362,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b7094c1bfe0dd687818b0b13305114577c797684","tid":2386648,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T17:15:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/828069721074704\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F828069721074704&d=mGfgamXUORjeED7mKz2VH4jkqoP0ISDA%2F8fQ3RVu%2FF4%3D&h=d949ae0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/828069721074704</a><br />\n<br />\n患有直腸癌四期的社運人士古思堯去年在法庭外聲援民主派人士期間，展示被塗污的國旗，昨（28 日）被判「侮辱國旗罪」罪成，即時入獄 4 個月。裁判官休庭前向古思堯表示，獄中的治療不比醫院遜色，並稱「本席希望你早日康復」。<br />\n<br />\n作為上一代首批投身香港社運的抗爭者，現年 71 歲的古思堯從左派熱血青年，到與日本妹拍拖的風騷民族舞老師，再成為了今天癌症末期還被判入冊的白髮老人，到底抗爭對他而言，還有甚麼意義？<br />\n<br />\n專訪全文：<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%85%A5%E7%8D%84%E5%89%8D%E5%B0%88%E8%A8%AA-%E7%99%8C%E7%97%87%E6%9C%AB%E6%9C%9F%E8%BF%8E%E7%AC%AC%E5%8D%81%E6%AC%A1%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E7%9B%A3-%E5%8F%A4%E6%80%9D%E5%A0%AF%E7%9A%84%E7%81%AB%E7%B4%85%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F-%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E5%9C%A8%E6%95%85%E6%88%91%E5%9C%A8/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2585%25A5%25E7%258D%2584%25E5%2589%258D%25E5%25B0%2588%25E8%25A8%25AA-%25E7%2599%258C%25E7%2597%2587%25E6%259C%25AB%25E6%259C%259F%25E8%25BF%258E%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E5%258D%2581%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E7%259B%25A3-%25E5%258F%25A4%25E6%2580%259D%25E5%25A0%25AF%25E7%259A%2584%25E7%2581%25AB%25E7%25B4%2585%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2594%259F-%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2588%25AD%25E5%259C%25A8%25E6%2595%2585%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%259C%25A8%2F&d=mGfgamXUORjeED7mKz2VH4jkqoP0ISDA%2F8fQ3RVu%2FF4%3D&h=563d1a91\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2F